metadata.name: Blame Summer
metadata.description:
" Blame Summer "

The season is changing ,
And the new one taking its place ,

"Cherry blossom is falling, Cherry blossom is on its way out, Hear a new word is calling, It hears me too and it wants me to shout it out"

Watercolour Painting on Arches Paper

11.7 in × 16.5 in
3312 × 4646 pixel PNG 300 dpi

The Primary Bidder can request for the physical painting.
